    <item>
      <title>有组织犯罪正在通过欧洲房地产洗钱</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-05/organized-crime-is-laundering-money-through-european-real-estate</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据一份关于整个地区有组织犯罪的报告，欧盟超过三分之一最具威胁的犯罪网络正在通过房地产洗钱。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-05/organized-crime-is-laundering-money-through-european-real-estate</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Apr 2024 06:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度最大反对党国大党在宣言中承诺提供就业机会和农民福利</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-05/india-opposition-party-pledges-jobs-farmer-welfare-in-manifesto</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度最大的反对党周五在全球最大规模选举前两周发布了政治宣言，承诺提供更多就业支持和农民收入。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-05/india-opposition-party-pledges-jobs-farmer-welfare-in-manifesto</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Apr 2024 06:22:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>台湾称援助已送达数百名因地震而受困的人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-05/taiwan-says-aid-reaching-hundreds-of-people-stranded-by-quake</link>
      <description><![CDATA[台湾官员表示，援助正在流向台湾东部数百人，他们在1999年以来最严重的地震中仍因道路封闭和废墟而受困。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-05/taiwan-says-aid-reaching-hundreds-of-people-stranded-by-quake</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Apr 2024 06:21:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>土耳其加入北约盟国暂停欧洲武器条约</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-05/turkey-joins-nato-allies-in-suspending-europe-arms-treaty</link>
      <description><![CDATA[土耳其暂停了一项对欧洲常规军事装备施加限制的武器条约，加入了北约盟国的行列，在俄罗斯去年退出该协议后，土耳其也采取了同样的做法。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-05/turkey-joins-nato-allies-in-suspending-europe-arms-treaty</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Apr 2024 06:11:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>抗议和价格上涨推动欧洲重新制定绿色协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-05/protests-and-prices-push-europe-into-remaking-its-green-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[2019年底，欧盟启动了绿色协议，旨在引领世界进入可持续的未来。然后是新冠疫情、通胀飙升、供应链断裂和俄罗斯入侵乌克兰。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-05/protests-and-prices-push-europe-into-remaking-its-green-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Apr 2024 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>耶伦抨击中国对美国企业采取“强制”行动，敦促改革</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-05/yellen-starts-china-tour-with-warning-on-factory-overcapacity</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国财政部长珍妮特·耶伦在对中国进行为期四天的访问之初，谴责中国政府对美国和其他外国公司的“不公平”待遇，并呼吁北京回归过去的亲市场改革。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-05/yellen-starts-china-tour-with-warning-on-factory-overcapacity</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Apr 2024 03:06:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>袜子排压安瓦尔引发汽油炸弹袭击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/petrol-bomb-attacks-on-malaysian-supermart-raise-heat-on-anwar</link>
      <description><![CDATA[马来西亚便利店连锁店因侮辱伊斯兰教而遭到袭击，这可能会动摇这个穆斯林占多数的国家总理安瓦尔·易卜拉欣(Anwar Ibrahim)脆弱的联盟。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/petrol-bomb-attacks-on-malaysian-supermart-raise-heat-on-anwar</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 22:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列辩论在苏纳克暴躁的内阁中掀起了新的裂痕</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/israel-arms-debate-opens-fresh-rift-in-sunak-s-fractious-cabinet</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列无人机袭击加沙，造成七名援助人员死亡其中包括三名英国人——随着英国首相暂停向特拉维夫出售武器的压力越来越大，这暴露了里希·苏纳克(Rishi Sunak)内阁中的新裂痕。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/israel-arms-debate-opens-fresh-rift-in-sunak-s-fractious-cabinet</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 19:27:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
